    <item>
      <title>宾夕法尼亚州选举诉讼激增表明它为何是头等大事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/pennsylvania-election-lawsuit-surge-shows-why-it-s-a-top-prize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚州正成为竞争激烈的总统竞选中的头彩之地，选举前夕，唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯都在这里疯狂竞选，双方的法律案件也随之激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/pennsylvania-election-lawsuit-surge-shows-why-it-s-a-top-prize</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普过早宣布赢得 2024 年大选引发担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/expected-delays-prompt-worry-over-trump-declaring-premature-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国即将迎来又一场旷日持久且可能存在争议的选举结果，一个问题笼罩着华盛顿各地的办公室、纽约的新闻机构和硅谷的社交网络：如果唐纳德·特朗普再次过早地宣布自己获胜，会发生什么？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/expected-delays-prompt-worry-over-trump-declaring-premature-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯在 2024 年大选最后冲刺中展现宾夕法尼亚爱意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trump-says-election-ours-to-lose-as-candidates-mobilize-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯正在竞选的最后一天举办一系列活动，希望在这场有望成为现代史上最接近的总统选举之一的选举前激发支持者的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trump-says-election-ours-to-lose-as-candidates-mobilize-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 17:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多要求石油、天然气生产商减少 35% 的排放量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trudeau-to-order-oil-gas-producers-to-cut-emissions-by-35</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府将要求加拿大的石油和天然气行业将排放量在 2019 年的基础上减少 35%，这项政策将加剧该国与西部省份的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/trudeau-to-order-oil-gas-producers-to-cut-emissions-by-35</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚将限制投票权以阻止俄罗斯影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/estonia-to-curb-voting-rights-in-bid-to-deter-russian-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚将推进旨在剥夺俄罗斯和白俄罗斯公民在地方选举中投票权的计划，此举旨在打击政府认为的亲克里姆林宫的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/estonia-to-curb-voting-rights-in-bid-to-deter-russian-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>令人震惊的民意调查显示哈里斯在爱荷华州领先，激发了州民主党人的热情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/harris-late-iowa-surge-energizes-democrats-in-republican-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“不要在爱荷华州睡觉”不仅仅是她蓝色T恤上的座右铭，爱荷华州众议院民主党领袖詹妮弗·康弗斯特向聚集在沃基当地党总部地下室的卡玛拉·哈里斯支持者高喊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/harris-late-iowa-surge-energizes-democrats-in-republican-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:16:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨敦促争吵不休的联盟着眼于切实可行的解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/scholz-urges-squabbling-alliance-to-focus-on-practical-solutions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨敦促执政联盟伙伴关注德国面临的挑战的务实解决方案，而不是“意识形态”，并搁置如何帮助欧洲最大经济体走出低迷的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/scholz-urges-squabbling-alliance-to-focus-on-practical-solutions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英格兰大学学费将自 2017 年以来首次上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/england-university-tuition-fees-to-rise-next-year-with-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于基尔·斯塔默政府试图解决高等教育领域的巨大资金压力，英格兰的大学学费明年将随着通货膨胀而上涨，这是自 2017 年以来的首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/england-university-tuition-fees-to-rise-next-year-with-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默呼吁世界像对待恐怖主义一样对待人口走私</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/starmer-urges-world-to-treat-people-smugglers-like-terrorists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 敦促国际盟友像对待恐怖分子一样对待人口走私者，同时他试图对非法移民采取强硬路线，这一政策问题导致西方国家的右翼支持率激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/starmer-urges-world-to-treat-people-smugglers-like-terrorists</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:09:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
